## ğŸŒ What is Software Development?

> **Software Development** is the process of creating, designing, deploying, and supporting software. It involves a set of activities that result in software products being delivered to end-users. ğŸ’¾

ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ’» It includes:
- Writing & maintaining source code
- Designing software architecture
- Testing & debugging
- Deployment & support

